name: Small Worm
desc:
Mindin' its own business.
Sould you interfere?

name: Stinky Rat
desc:
*sniffs around maniacally*
*runs towards you*

name: Rat Duo
desc:
It is getting out of hand.
Now there are two of them.

name: Momma Boar
desc:
It follows you around.
No matter what you do.

name: Eight-legged Menace
desc:
Always appears out of nowhere.
A little bit more scary at night.

name: Swarm of Bees
desc:
No matter what you do.
You stay totally surrounded.

name: Ring of Love
desc:
Keeps your heart warm.
Could bring back lost memories.
message: You felt a surge in your chest

name: Cinnamon Cookie
desc:
This cookie looks super tasty.
Give me that!

name: Old Wolf
desc:
It walks slowly towards you.
Hopefully it's not hungry.

name: Giant Web
desc:
Hopefully nobody's home.
It seems quite sturdy.
message: You entangled yourself with a spider

name: Lumberjack Axe
desc:
The owner is probably nearby.
I'd rather not mess with it.
message: The owner jumped out and hit you

name: Old Scroll
desc:
Some say these will make you blind.
There's only one way to find out.

name: Glowing Potion
desc:
It has a sinister aura.
You probably shouldn't drink it.
message: It left funny taste in your mouth

name: Curious Raccoon
desc:
Aaaaw. Look at him.
A little cute boy.

name: Bow and Arrows
desc:
There must be a huntsman around.
He probably won't miss it.

name: Extra Big Snake
desc:
Wow! This guy has been eatin' a lot.
Maybe you could use it as a rope.

name: Smart Owl
desc:
Why is there an owl during daytime?
You should investigate.
message: It revealed you a powerful secret

name: Abandoned Tent
desc:
Nice and cozy place to rest.
You could use a break.
message: You landed in a swarm of fleas

name: Suspicious Mushroom
desc:
Looks really tasty.
Could be eaten raw.

name: Lost Sheep
desc:
Oooh. It must've lost its herd.
I should try to lead it back.

name: Ring of Damage
desc:
Does something with damage.
Hopefully in a good way.
message: Ouch! The ring is too tight

name: Nervous Deer
desc:
Something is not right.
You must be very careful.

name: Wild Carrot
desc:
Sometimes even the simplest things
can heal your body and soul.

name: Spruce Tree
desc:
Another tree in a forest.
You never noticed it before.

name: Oak Tree
desc:
Another tree in a forest.
Who would have thought?

name: Fern Bush
desc:
It is covered with an interesting pattern.
Hopefully it's not toxic.

name: Roasted Chicken
desc:
It is still hot and untouched.
Who would leave it like that?

name: Spiky Hedgehog
desc:
At first it looked like a stone.
Then it started moving.

name: Rose Flower Bush
desc:
These are just beautiful.
You should grab some.
message: Ouch! It has a lot of thorns

name: Bottomless Hole
desc:
You wonder whats in there.
Maybe some treasure?.
message: Ouch! It was deeper than expected

name: Sentient Fox
desc:
It doesn't seem scared of you.
Could it be friend?
message: It gave you an agility training

name: Wrinkled Map
desc:
You stumbled upon an old map.
There are some notes around the edges.

name: Little Bird
desc:
It doesn't look any dangerous.
But you can never know.
